Usage: get_constant_for_timing [-help] <pin_name> [-bidi_input  | -bidi_output ]

-help           # Prints out the command usage
<pin_name>      # Name of the single pin to query for pin state
                # (string, required)
-bidi_input     # Returns the constant that is set on the input part of
                # bidirectional pins (bool, optional)
-bidi_output    # Returns the constant that is set on the output part of
                # bidirectional pins (bool, optional)